lead_paragraph: When Rio opened its Olympic Park this month there was one thing conspicuously absent around the venues, walkways and public areas where visitors will gather to watch 16 sports in August: trees.

headline.print_headline: Treeless $656 Million Olympic Park in Rio a Concrete Jungle
